nd the rejecters of His </div><div class="t mde8 x70 h4 y477 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">atonement.&quot;—Patriarchs </div><div class="t m449 x17d h30 y477 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Prophets, </div><div class="t mce3 x56 h4 y6c1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages 339, 340. </div><div class="t me4 x78 h2d y70 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m6b7 x3d h2d y70 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What figure is used to repre-</div><div class="t mda5 x70 h2d y200 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sent the manifestation of the wrath </div><div class="t m13a6 x70 h2d ybf7 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God against the rejecters of His </div><div class="t m3c0 x70 h2d y22 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">message? Rev. 14:17-20. </div><div class="t m2bd xab h4 y381 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;He that ruleth in the heavens is </div><div class="t m41c x70 h4 y5c8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the One who sees the end from the begin-</div><div class="t m481 x70 h4 y10b2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ning,—the One before whom the mysteries </div><div class="t m2e9 x70 h4 y999 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the past and the future are alike out-</div><div class="t maaf x70 h4 y3f8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spread, and who, beyond the woe and </div><div class="t md17 x70 h4 y2ae ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">darkness and ruin that sin has wrought, </div><div class="t m8de x70 h4 y8ab ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beholds the accomplishment of His own </div><div class="t m176 x1f h1c y45a ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1</div><div class="t m18c0 x20 h4 y1af ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">26</div><div class="t ma7e x21 h1c y1af ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 </div><div class="t md43 x6e h1c y1af ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
